title: New: Queue – Frontier
body:
Big fan of the energy on this new track from DC four piece **Queue**.

There’s definitely an element of Aussie outfit Middle Kids to the songwriting, yet _Frontier_ manages to really carve out a niche of it’s own; proving unrelenting and full of an in your face dynamism that makes for such an intoxicating listen. Check it out below.
